snippet.title: Amber Heard officially confirmed as Mera in The Justice League!!!
snippet.description:
What's up, guys, welcome back to another DC filled video here on the EdWord where I'll be discussing my thoughts on the big announcement that came out yesterday that actress Amber Heard is indeed going to be playing Mera in The Justice League: Part One and the solo Aquaman movie. Thank you so much for watching, don't forget to subscribe and like my newly created Facebook page, the link is down below.

Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice finally arrives March 25th and The Justice League: Part One hits theaters Nov 17, 2017 

https://www.facebook.com/theedword2016/
